    Cone Radius Function using sapply

    cone_radius_sapply.Rd

    Functions for calculating the radius of the cone using different approaches.

    cone_radius_sapply(x_values)

    Arguments

    x_values

    Numeric vector of heights.

    Value

    A numeric vector of radii.

    Author

    Sofia Daza

    Examples

    cone_radius_for(seq(0, 10, length.out = 100))
